Package packlightbulb

  • Interface Summary
    Interface Description
    security
    The security interface implements a security level checker for leds that can be placed in wet places.
  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    Adjustable
    Represents an adjustable light bulb
    Fluorescent
    Represents a fluorescent light bulb.
    Halogen
    Represents an halogen light bulb.
    Incandescent
    Represents an incandescent light bulb.
    Led
    Represents a LED light bulb.
    LightBulb
    Represents a light bulb in general.
    NonIncandescent
    Represents a non incandescent light bulb.
  • Exception Summary
    Exception Description
    AlreadyOffException
    Thrown if an attempt is made to turn off a light bulb that is already off.
    AlreadyOnException
    Thrown if an attempt is made to turn on a light bulb that is already on.
    UnknownIdentifierException
    Thrown when a LightBulb ID that does not match any LightBulb ID on an ArrayList is given.
